name: git_diff
description: Compare commits, branches, and files with git diff — a full diff between two refs, a per-file summary, just the changed filenames, and a word-level diff. Use to see what a branch changed, review before committing, or get the list of files a range touched.
kind: tool
tags: [git, diff, compare, branch, stat, review]
use_when: [diff two branches, what changed between commits, list files changed in a range, summary of changes, word level diff, review changes before commit, compare a file across commits]
